Part 3: BC Labels (brief)
Biocultural Labels parallel TK Labels but focus on biodiversity and genetic resources. They include BC Provenance (BC P), BC Multiple Provenance (BC MP), BC Consent Verified (BC CV), BC Consent Non-Verified (BC CNV), BC Research (BC R), BC Non-Commercial (BC NC), BC Commercialization (BC C), BC Outreach (BC O), and BC Open to Collaboration (BC CB). Use these for entries where the maritime ecological knowledge dimension is primary. Full reference: localcontexts.org/labels/biocultural-labels.

